page.title: 14SECONDARY SCHOOL
page.content: I am looking forward to Secondary School because you can make new friends and see new teachers. I also like it because you have to go to different classrooms for different subjects.My favourite subject is cookery because I like making food.I go to Latymer by two buses and as my brother goes to that school I can go with him. Latymer is a large school,I will not be able to find my way around for the first week. I am the only person going to Latymer this year so I will have to make a lot of new friends. In the first year I will be learning German and in the second year I will be learning German.
